reut2-003.sgm, KINGDOM OF SWEDEN ISSUES 100 MLN STG BOND, Kingdom of Sweden is issuing a 100 mlnstg bond due April 15, 1997 carrying a coupon of 9-1/2 pct andpriced at 101-1/4, said Baring Brothers and Co Ltd as leadmanager.    The issue is payable on April 15, 1987.    The bond is callable after seven years at 100-1/8 pct andit will be listed on the London Stock Exchange. Fees are a1-3/8 pct selling concession and 5/8 pct combined managementand underwriting fee. REUTER&#3;
