reut2-003.sgm, ROLLS ROYCE SEEKS 250 MLN STG CREDIT FACILITY, Rolls Royce, the U.K.'s state-owned carand aircraft engine maker, is seeking a 250 mln stg multipleoption facility to provide it with additional sources offinancing, banking sources said.    They said the facility, which will be syndicated among asmall group of the borrower's relationship banks, is being putin place ahead of the privatisation of Rolls Royce in April orMay. At the borrower's request, terms will not be discloseduntil later this week, when bankers expect the syndication toclose. But while the terms are in line with the market, theyare somewhat tight, bankers said. Reuter&#3;
