reut2-003.sgm, ASCS BUYS PROCESSED PRODUCTS FOR DOMESTIC USE, The Agricultural Stabilization andConservation Service (ASCS) bought 25.7 mln pounds of wheatflour at a cost of 2.8 mln dlrs for domestic shipment April1-15 and April 16-30, an ASCS spokesman said.    ASCS also bought 11.1 mln pounds of bakers flour for 1.1mln dlrs, 1.9 mln pounds of pasta for 408,258 dlrs, 1.4 mlnpounds of processed cereal products for 304,043 dlrs, 4.8 mlnpounds of corn products for 474,944 dlrs, and 16.3 mln poundsof milled rice for 2.0 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;
