reut2-003.sgm, AXLON &lt;AXLN> NAMES CO-CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER, Axlon Inc said Austin C.Marshall has been named president and co-chief executiveofficer, sharing power in the latter post with founder andchairman Nolan K. Bushnell.    The company said Marshall, who had been executive vicepresident of New York toy company Playtime, will haveresponsibility for the distribution of toys and Bushnell willconcentrate on research and development and licensing. Reuter&#3;
