reut2-003.sgm, SECURITIES DEALER HAS LEASEWAY &lt;LTC> STAKE, Alpine Associates, a Cresskill, N.J.securities dealer, told the Securities and Exchange Commissionit has acquired 565,100 shares of Leaseway TransportCorp, or 5.9 pct of the total outstanding common stock.    Alpine, a limited partnership, said it bought the stock for28.1 mln dlrs as an investment in the ordinary course of itsbusiness as a securities dealer.    It left open the possibility that it might buy moreLeaseway stock or sell some or all of its current stake, butsaid it has no plans to seek control of the company. Reuter&#3;
