reut2-003.sgm, CITIZENS FIDELITY &lt;CFDY> PAPER UPGRADED BY S/P, Standard and Poor's Corp said itraised to A-1-plus from A-1 the commercial paper of CitizensFidelity Corp and its unit Citizens Fidelity Bank and Trust.    S and P cited the completion of the firm's merger with PNCFinancial Corp &lt;PNCF>, saying PNC has shown solid earnings,excellent liquidity and a conservative capital position.    The rating agency also upgraded long-term debt supported byletters of credit of lead bank Citizens Fidelity Bank toAA-plus from A. The bank's certificates of deposit were uppedto AA-plus and A-1-plus from A and A-1 respectively. Reuter&#3;
